flowchart TD
  A[Start Build] --> B[Compile Source]
  B --> C[Test Suite]
  C --> D{Tests Passed?}
  D -->|No| E[Notify Developer]
  E --> A
  D -->|Yes| F[Build Docker Image]

  subgraph Deploy Pipeline
    F --> G[Deploy to Staging]
